We've decided that we will not be doing another DirtCar Giveaway in 2020.
In the last 3 years, www.DirtCarUSA.com has given away 2 RACE READY Racecars, $15,000 cash, and over $30,000 in gift cards/parts to racers.  All while doing it legally (not illegal raffles) which requires a lot of legal costs & time.

For 2020, we've decided that we want a program that benefits every single customer & hopefully makes every driver faster that participates, not just one that benefits the few winners.
With that being said, more details will be released at a later date!
Feel free to comment any questions you have!
Thanks.

Super Nationals 2019 results:
230 cars this year.

Night #1: Started Last in our heat, ran 1st.
Started 4th in the Amain, ran 5th.

Night #2: Started 5th in our heat, ran 3rd.
Started 5th in the Bmain, ran 2nd.

Night #3: Started 1st in our heat, ran 2nd.
Started 18th in the Amain, ran 12th.

Night #4: Started 1st in our heat, was leading until the rain came in and the race was called.
Started on the pole of the Amain qualifier, car struggled in the tack/grease after a heavy rain, pushed outta the racing line and outta the transfer spot into the Big Dance. 
All-in-all, a pretty good time... we'll get er' in the show next year!
